  "body": "The current signature of the validator's `deposit` function has both `bytes[32]` and `bytes32` parameters:\r\n\r\n```\r\ndef deposit(pubkey: bytes[PUBKEY_LENGTH],\r\n            withdrawal_credentials: bytes[WITHDRAWAL_CREDENTIALS_LENGTH],\r\n            signature: bytes[SIGNATURE_LENGTH],\r\n            deposit_data_root: bytes32):\r\n```\r\n\r\nWould it not make sense to have the final parameter be `bytes[32]` so that it is consistent?",
